<html xmlns:o='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office' xmlns:w='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40'><head><meta charset='utf-8'><title>Text To Word</title></head><body><p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Target Architecture (ChatGPT-like Voice UX)</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">┌─────────────┐ │ Microphone │ └─────┬───────┘ │ (stream audio frames) ▼ ┌──────────────────────┐ │ Streaming Speech-to- │ &larr; partial text (live) │ Text (Whisper / STT) │ └─────┬────────────────┘ │ (partial text chunks) ▼ ┌───────────────────────────────┐ │ OpenAI Realtime / Streaming │ &larr; streaming tokens │ LLM (WebSocket / SSE) │ └─────┬─────────────────────────┘ │ (token-by-token output) ▼ ┌──────────────────────┐ │ Streaming Text-to- │ &larr; generate audio chunks │ Speech (TTS) │ └─────┬────────────────┘ │ ▼ ┌─────────────┐ │ Audio Player│ &larr; play while generating └─────────────┘</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Nothing waits for completion. Everything streams.</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">---</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">🧩 Best Stack for Flutter (2025-ready)</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">1️⃣ Audio capture (low latency)</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Use PCM audio frames (16kHz)</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Send frames every ~20&ndash;40 ms</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Flutter</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">flutter_sound</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">audio_streamer</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">mic_stream</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">---</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">2️⃣ Streaming Speech-to-Text (critical)</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">✅ Best options</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Option A (Best): OpenAI Realtime STT</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Uses WebSockets</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Emits partial transcripts</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Very low latency</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Option B: Whisper (Streaming mode)</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Self-hosted or cloud</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Slightly more latency</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Still usable if chunked properly</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">⚠️ Do NOT wait for full audio before STT.</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">---</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">3️⃣ Streaming LLM response (MOST IMPORTANT)</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">❌ REST /chat/completions &rarr; slow ✅ Streaming responses</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Best choice</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">OpenAI Realtime API (WebSocket)</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Token-level streaming</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Can be interrupted mid-sentence</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">This is exactly what ChatGPT Voice uses.</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">---</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">4️⃣ Streaming Text-to-Speech (don&rsquo;t wait!)</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">❌ Generate full audio &rarr; play ✅ Generate audio chunks &rarr; play immediately</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Best choices:</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">OpenAI TTS (streaming)</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Or native Android TTS (very fast)</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Or ElevenLabs streaming TTS</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">---</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">🔥 The MAGIC: Full-Duplex Conversation</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">What makes it feel &ldquo;alive&rdquo;</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">✔ Continuous listening</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Mic is always ON</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">User can interrupt the model</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">✔ Barge-in support</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">If user starts talking:</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Stop TTS playback immediately</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Cancel current LLM generation</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Switch to listening mode</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">This alone makes your app feel 10&times; smarter.</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">---</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">🧠 Conversation Loop (real logic)</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">while (app is active): listen to mic stream audio &rarr; STT if partial text detected: send partial text &rarr; LLM if LLM tokens arrive: stream tokens &rarr; TTS play audio immediately if user speaks again: interrupt TTS cancel LLM</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">---</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">⚙️ Flutter Implementation Strategy</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Architecture layers</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">presentation/ ├─ voice_ui.dart core/ ├─ audio_stream_service.dart ├─ stt_service.dart ├─ llm_realtime_service.dart ├─ tts_stream_service.dart state/ ├─ voice_session_provider.dart (Riverpod)</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Use Riverpod / StateNotifier to manage:</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Listening</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Thinking</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Speaking</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Interrupted</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">---</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">🚀 Best OpenAI Setup (Recommended)</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">If you want BEST possible UX</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Use:</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">OpenAI Realtime API (WebSocket)</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Streaming STT + LLM + TTS</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">One persistent connection</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">This is exactly how ChatGPT Voice works.</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">---</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Latency comparison (realistic)</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Approach Latency</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Record &rarr; REST &rarr; Speak ❌ 3&ndash;6 sec Chunked STT + REST LLM ⚠️ 1.5&ndash;2 sec Streaming STT + Streaming LLM ✅ 300&ndash;600 ms Realtime API (full duplex) 🔥 ~200 ms</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">---</p>
<p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Completely build this archiecture in flutter and make it optimized</p></body></html>